content.p: We invite you to participate in the programme to combine native intelligence with Emotional Intelligence to increase your ability to successfully manage the constant change. The pace of the world increases and our environment makes more and more demand on our cognitive, emotional and physical resources, Emotional Intelligence is increasingly critical as a skill set. If you are interested to participate, drop us a note. For further information, please contact Ms. Salinee Ganeson at +603 8925 8305 or +603 8725 3665. telephone: +6 (03) 8924 8373 fax: +6 (03) 8924 8657 email: alumnirelations@nottingham.edu.my
